## COMMON PATTERNS TO AVOID

### âŒ NEVER DO THIS:
```jsx
// âŒ Using pure black/white
<div className="bg-white text-black">

// âŒ Using left/right directly
<div className="ml-4 mr-8">

// âŒ Exposing API keys in frontend
const NOTION_KEY = "secret_xxx";

// âŒ Animating width/height/left/right
.element { transition: left 0.3s; }

// âŒ Rounded corners everywhere
<div className="rounded-lg">

// âŒ Subtle shadows
<div className="shadow-sm">

// âŒ Missing RTL direction
<div className="flex flex-row">

// âŒ English placeholder in Hebrew input
<input placeholder="Search..." />

// âŒ Hard-coded strings instead of Hebrew
<h1>Welcome to Design Hub</h1>
```

### âœ… ALWAYS DO THIS:
```jsx
// âœ… Using off-black/off-white
<div className="bg-off-white text-off-black">

// âœ… Using logical properties
<div className="ms-4 me-8">

// âœ… API keys in backend only
// In .env: NOTION_API_KEY=secret_xxx

// âœ… Animating transforms
.element { transition: transform 0.3s; }

// âœ… No rounded corners (or blocky only)
<div className=""> or <div className="rounded-none">

// âœ… Thick brutalist shadows
<div className="shadow-brutalist">

// âœ… RTL flex with reverse
<div className="flex flex-row-reverse">

// âœ… Hebrew placeholder
<input placeholder="×—×™×¤×•×©..." />

// âœ… Hebrew strings
<h1>×‘×¨×•×›×™× ×”×‘××™× ×œ××‘ ×”×¢×™×¦×•×‘</h1>
```

